<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport"
          content="width=device-width, user-scalable=no, initial-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0, minimum-scale=1.0">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="ie=edge">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.4.1/css/bootstrap.min.css" integrity="sha384-Vkoo8x4CGsO3+Hhxv8T/Q5PaXtkKtu6ug5TOeNV6gBiFeWPGFN9MuhOf23Q9Ifjh" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Indie+Flower&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/assets/css/FakePage.css">
    <title>Kitty Adopt </title>
</head>
<body>
<header>
<nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-danger bg-danger">
    <h3 class="navbar-brand">Kitty Adopt !</h3>
    <div class="collapse navbar-collapse text-right" id="navbarNavAltMarkup">
        <div class="navbar-nav">
            <a class="nav-item nav-link ml-5 mr-5" href="#adopt">Adopt</a>
            {% if session.kittenadopt == true %}<a class="nav-item nav-link ml-5 " href="#kitten">View kitten</a> {% endif %}
        </div>
    </div>
</nav>
</header>
<div class="bloc_page">
    <h1> Welcome on Kitty Adopt !</h1>
    <div id="carouselExampleIndicators" class="carousel slide" data-ride="carousel">
        <ol class="carousel-indicators">
            <li data-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-slide-to="0" class="active"></li>
            <li data-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-slide-to="1"></li>
            <li data-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-slide-to="2"></li>
        </ol>
        <div class="carousel-inner">
            <div class="carousel-item active">
                <img class="d-block w-100" src="/assets/images/index_img/chat3.jpg" alt="First slide">
            </div>
            <div class="carousel-item">
                <img class="d-block w-100" src="/assets/images/index_img/chat1.jpg" alt="Second slide">
            </div>
            <div class="carousel-item">
                <img class="d-block w-100" src="/assets/images/index_img/chat2.jpg" alt="Third slide">
            </div>
        </div>
        <a class="carousel-control-prev" href="#carouselExampleIndicators" role="button" data-slide="prev">
            <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
            <span class="sr-only">Previous</span>
        </a>
        <a class="carousel-control-next" href="#carouselExampleIndicators" role="button" data-slide="next">
            <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
            <span class="sr-only">Next</span>
        </a>
    </div>
    <h1>Choose one..</h1>
    <div class="card-deck" id="adopt">
        <div class="card">
            <img class="card-img-top" src="https://www.wikichat.fr/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/Fotolia_83534551_S.jpg" alt="Card image cap">
            <div class="card-body">
                <h5 class="card-title">Tony</h5>
                <p class="card-text">Tony is a seducer. A lot of Kitten love him, so why not you ?</p>
            </div>
            <div class="card-footer">
                <small class="text-muted"><form method="post"> <button type="submit" name="KittenChoice">Adopt !</button></form></small>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
            <img class="card-img-top" src="https://static.wamiz.fr/images/news/medium/kangacarre.jpg" alt="Card image cap">
            <div class="card-body">
                <h5 class="card-title">Bobby</h5>
                <p class="card-text">When Bobby say, we listen. When Bobby give you a kiss, you take him ! (The kiss, not the Kitten, or he will bite you)</p>
            </div>
            <div class="card-footer">
                <small class="text-muted"><form method="post"> <button type="submit" name="KittenChoice">Adopt !</button></form></small>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
            <img class="card-img-top" src="https://static.wamiz.fr/images/news/medium/1482753_1440711789479320_478071385_n.jpg" alt="Card image cap">
            <div class="card-body">
                <h5 class="card-title">Jack</h5>
                <p class="card-text">This is a long Story with Jack... We find him in a club where he spend a lot of money sometimes. Don't try to play with him. </p>
            </div>
            <div class="card-footer">
                <small class="text-muted"><form method="post"> <button type="submit" name="KittenChoice">Adopt !</button></form></small>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="card-deck">
        <div class="card">
            <img class="card-img-top" src="https://assets.change.org/photos/8/mg/iv/VRmgIVdbVhmvBgW-400x400-noPad.jpg?1522337464" alt="Card image cap">
            <div class="card-body">
                <h5 class="card-title">Toasty</h5>
                <p class="card-text">This is kitten is very sweeeeet ! But he eat a lot ! </p>
            </div>
            <div class="card-footer">
                <small class="text-muted"><form method="post"> <button type="submit" name="KittenChoice">Adopt !</button></form></small>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
            <img class="card-img-top" src="https://static.wamiz.fr/images/news/medium/73304_274769032659524_1245793394_n.jpg" alt="Card image cap">
            <div class="card-body">
                <h5 class="card-title">Casimodo</h5>
                <p class="card-text">This kitten was arrested for drug trafic. But he still cute (and standing).</p>
            </div>
            <div class="card-footer">
                <small class="text-muted"><form method="post"> <button type="submit" name="KittenChoice">Adopt !</button></form></small>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
            <img class="card-img-top" src="https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn%3AANd9GcRQztMFBX3o_eX4-dmZN46LFCExiBcNqCoTZ3S4moGo9zVAGHJb&usqp=CAU" alt="Card image cap">
            <div class="card-body">
                <h5 class="card-title">Jean-Pierre du Chateau au Lac de Montegure</h5>
                <p class="card-text">Like Jean-Pierre say "Saucer avec son pain n'est pas convenable".</p>
            </div>
            <div class="card-footer">
                <small class="text-muted"><form method="post"> <button type="submit" name="KittenChoice">Adopt !</button></form></small>
            </div>
        </div>
        {% if session.kittenadopt == true %}
    </div>
    <div class="card">
        <h5 class="card-header" id="kitten">You adopt a new kitten</h5>
        <div class="card-body end_bloc">
            <h5 class="card-title">He is hungry.. </h5>
            <img class="img-responsive" width="30%" height="30%" src="/assets/images/index_img/kitten.gif">
            <a href="/Login/login" class="btn btn-primary btn-danger">Give him some food ! </a>
        </div>
    </div>
    {% endif %}
</div>
<footer id="sticky-footer" class="py-4 bg-dark text-white-50">
    <div class="container text-center">
        <small> © 2020 made by Anaïs, Elhadj, Johnny, Sandrine, Sten </small>
    </div>
</footer>
<script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.4.1.slim.min.js" integrity="sha384-J6qa4849blE2+poT4WnyKhv5vZF5SrPo0iEjwBvKU7imGFAV0wwj1yYfoRSJoZ+n" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
<script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/popper.js@1.16.0/dist/umd/popper.min.js" integrity="sha384-Q6E9RHvbIyZFJoft+2mJbHaEWldlvI9IOYy5n3zV9zzTtmI3UksdQRVvoxMfooAo" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
<script src="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.4.1/js/bootstrap.min.js" integrity="sha384-wfSDF2E50Y2D1uUdj0O3uMBJnjuUD4Ih7YwaYd1iqfktj0Uod8GCExl3Og8ifwB6" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
</body>
</html>